========
s2stools
========

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/s2stools/badge/?version=latest
    :target: https://s2stools.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
    :alt: Documentation Status


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/s2stools.svg
